item.title: [HIVE-20294] Vectorization: Fix NULL / Wrong Results issues in COALESCE / ELT
item.description:
Write new UT tests that use random data and intentional isRepeating batches to checks for NULL and Wrong Results for vectorized COALESCE and ELT.

Also, add tests for ARRAY and MAP indexing, IS [NOT] NULL and NOT
item.summary: Vectorization: Fix NULL / Wrong Results issues in COALESCE / ELT
